<paragraph blockId="32.[227,1436,1166,1228]" pageId="32" pageNumber="99">
Species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Miller, Dunbar &amp; Condra" authorityYear="1933" box="[365,536,1167,1192]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Trigonoceratidae" genus="Maccoyoceras" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Nautilida" pageId="32" pageNumber="99" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[365,536,1167,1192]" italics="true" pageId="32" pageNumber="99">Maccoyoceras</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with subquadrate whorl profile (ww/wh ~1.05), venter slightly flattened, ventrolateral shoulder broadly rounded. Whorls not embracing.
</paragraph>
